title: get column label from meta data object should return user recognizable strings
OB: Currently, when calling IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before data extraction, it is not returning user recognizable strings.
EB: When I call IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before data extraction, it should return user recognizable strings that match the labels displayed after extraction.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Call IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before data extraction.
2. Compare the results with the labels displayed after data extraction.
